N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5003.1 - Applicability

State Regulations

The provisions of this Part shall apply to all lottery
draw games. In all events, the determination of prize winners shall be subject
to the ticket validation requirements as set forth in this

Part. Notes
